title: Start
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Hi Ji-Yeon, I'm Won, not Wonbo because it's our first time meeting.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Hi! It's nice to meet you this is a surprise.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
This other girl I met online blew off our first meeting...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Huh. She sounds rude.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Right?!
Since this is definitely our first time speaking, let me ask you...
I just moved to the area. What is there to do around here?
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Yes, I have never spoken to you before.
Well, I recommend going to a Piston's game.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Awesome! So let me talk about myself for the next 15 minutes.

title: Wonbo
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Being single is not the worst thing in the world,
But having a girlfriend is so much better...
Especially if she is wife-material.
If only I could find someone that meets my high standards...
Wait a minute. Who is that??
